WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:01.440
Hi, Betty.

00:01.440 --> 00:02.800
Hi, Ling Ling.

00:02.800 --> 00:05.880
I'd like to see the traditional Beijing opera.

00:05.880 --> 00:09.280
Do you want to come to Laoshua Tea House with me?

00:09.280 --> 00:12.080
What's Laoshua Tea House?

00:12.080 --> 00:17.040
You can listen to the Beijing opera there and drink tea at the same time.

00:17.040 --> 00:18.440
Yes, please.

00:18.440 --> 00:20.080
I'd like to go with you.

00:20.080 --> 00:21.960
You can tell me what's happening.

00:21.960 --> 00:26.240
Yes, it's quite difficult to understand the story.

00:26.240 --> 00:28.720
Just watch the actors and actresses.

00:28.720 --> 00:32.000
Listen to the music and try to enjoy it.

